{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/STEAMGIF_Possession_600x306.gif?t=1737904410\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your powers of possession bring inanimate objects to life! Use them to fight, run away or just <strong><i>look darn good</i></strong> whilst you soak up the chaos unfolding around you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/STEAMGIF_Combat_600x306.gif?t=1737904410\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Polterguys is a spooky brawlfest where mischievous ghosts are being stalked by a deadly monster who wants to destroy them all! Chaotic? Yes! Competitive? You betcha!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/STEAMGIF_Whirlwind_600x306.gif?t=1737904410\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sabotage</strong> and spite are your greatest allies! Use the monster as a <strong>portable death machine</strong> to destroy your opponents with <i>seemingly</i> harmless abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/extras/STEAMGIF_Grenade_600x306.gif?t=1737904410\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are <strong>tonnes of powerups and traps</strong> sprinkled about the levels to help you create carnage... the question is can you <strong>make it count</strong> with the monster breathing down your little gooey neck?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">&quot;So... what's in the game <i><strong>RIGHT NOW!?&quot;</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We're glad you asked! Here's what you get on day one:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">8 unique levels packed with physics based traps and toys!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">20 collectable costume possessions to discover and level up!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our main mode 'Monster Mash' and 2 mini-modes 'Polterball' and 'Repossession'!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Daily and weekly challenges!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weekly leader boards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Spooky Trail to travel along for progression!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Loads of rewards: avatars, emotes, new special effects, personalised podiums, and way more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Split screen couch play for up to 4 players, who can also go online together and play as a party!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your own space called your 'haunt'... use candy that you collect to buy new addons for it in game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737904410","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/page.bg.jpg?t=1737904410","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/963172eea719bdb427832633a495ebd77cd7f861/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737904410","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1043520/963172eea719bdb427832633a495ebd77cd7f861/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737904410","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49}